Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist: Brotherhood
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 40
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,===============================================================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:38.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So you're suggesting Major General Armstrong had a hand in Lieutenant General Raven's disappearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:39.99,Default,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:43.54,Default,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure she left no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:44.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:50.16,Default,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well. Our job is to take over this fort...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:55.27,Default,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,...while that fox is being investigated in Central by a herd of tigers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.35,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it isn't the Major General.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.77,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe you were transferred to Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.15,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,What connections did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.77,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's simply an honest display of my capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.36,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Says the fresh meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:20.78,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.32,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I've been summoned by the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.70,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be able to return to Briggs for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:28.24,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,"For a while"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:31.47,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to have to take you to dinner at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.58,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your treat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:36.13,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll let me eat until you go bankrupt, I don't mind going for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.58,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll give up on the meal, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:41.92,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Both your wallet and your balls are pea-sized, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:45.16,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,How about some flowers instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:50.07,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There are many great florists in Central, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.60,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.11,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You may enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.11,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:12.12,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Major General Armstrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:16.50,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,...let me hear more about\NLieutenant General Raven's disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:18.76,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.44,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to hide this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:28.77,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a man as great as you choose to place a fool like Raven by his side?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.40,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,So you got rid of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.12,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:39.32,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Having a subordinate with such a loose tongue would do you no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:43.53,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,What did Lieutenant General Raven tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.41,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Something about an immortal army...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:48.88,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,...the history of this country, and your real identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:52.79,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,He told me many things I didn't even ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:59.04,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,So you still chose to respond to\Nmy summons after hearing all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:03.30,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, to request the seat the idiot had been placing his ass on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:09.01,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting, as expected of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:13.65,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. You may have the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:18.65,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I'll have one of my men govern over Briggs. Are you fine with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.86,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:24.40,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,They are powerful soldiers I trained with great care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:27.03,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:32.79,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting. Do your best, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:40.67,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,"Nothing ventured, nothing gained."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.92,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,So the Major General ventured into the enemy's lair by her own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.43,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This place also belongs to them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.08,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,But they're unaware...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:59.90,Default,Hen,0000,0000,0000,,...Briggs is a giant monolith that can act with a united will, even if its master happens to be away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:04.69,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, it's a war between bears and tigers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.49,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Is that seat free?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:17.62,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.21,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,How's your work progressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't finish everything unless I multitask during my meals, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:29.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:33.50,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much to memorize; I'm fairly busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:37.13,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,But the Führer President does his job very quickly, so I do not have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.65,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't loaf either, unlike a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.32,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling this topic is heading in a direction I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.32,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:55.96,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Scar is apparently up north.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:59.25,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,So are the Elric brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.17,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:07.26,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,My old classmates, Lucy and Ian, are also up north.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.88,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,They tell me many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:14.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, the north and the east will be holding joint exercises in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:19.64,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we've been defeated countless times by Major Miles and Captain Buccaneer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:22.74,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Miles... Buccaneer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:27.52,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,York, Ida, and Sugar, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:35.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Havoc, Oscar, Mike, Uni, Nora, Charley...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:38.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Uni again, then Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.95,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Uni comes again, then next... is Sterling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.95,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,"Selim Bradley is Homunculus".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:55.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no way that {\i1}can't{\i0\fscx30} {\r} be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:02.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is about to happen here in Central?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.26,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.45,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.16,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:21.67,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:24.79,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.64,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.09,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:34.55,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you at least a little surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.06,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,If I do get surprised, will you give me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.52,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're always at ease. I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.57,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.35,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Slave Number 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:48.37,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask for a number. I want your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.79,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a name. I'm a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:51.98,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Slave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:58.06,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,People who are stripped of their rights and freedom, and are exchanged as possessions in conveyance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.16,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Conveyance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:03.22,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,To transfer property and rights and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.21,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,You're not very bright, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.53,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:13.26,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand how I was born from someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:17.22,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who gave me blood, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:23.03,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,They did take a lot of blood from me to use for experiments...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:27.73,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I was born because you gave me blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:31.82,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:35.28,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,"Slave Number 23" just sounds too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.64,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a name, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.49,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:43.38,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want a cool name? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:47.86,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Teo... Teofrastus Bombastus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:47.86,Default-alt,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:54.21,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it can't be too long; else you won't be able to memorize it. You're dumb, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.43,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Quit saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.71,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about Van?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:00.78,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Van Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.72,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Van Hohen, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.54,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.13,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,You spell it like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.91,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, do you know how to read and write?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:12.73,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to know to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.57,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,The work of a slave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.35,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want freedom and rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:25.23,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan on ending your life as a slave without gaining basic human rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:31.12,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same as being in this stuffy flask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:36.34,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to share my knowledge with you, Van Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:43.27,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... What {\i1}are{\i0\fscx30} {\r} you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.54,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What should I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:51.69,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,The Little One Inside the Flask. So... call me "Homunculus".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:09.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All was created from one, and it eventually returns to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, one is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All exists due to one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,...and all exists within one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:21.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If one does not contain all, then there exists nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:24.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:28.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're now a fine alchemist, Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.03,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not good enough to be on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:35.55,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,My abilities are far beneath yours, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.29,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm really thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.69,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:45.91,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Because you gave me knowledge,\NI'm able to live a good life like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.57,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also happy to be in Master's favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:53.58,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It may be possible that I can marry someone in the future and start my own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:55.92,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,A family, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.16,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are inconvenient creatures, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:02.93,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,The species can't live on unless they all create a community and expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.81,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:10.44,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It may be stupid in your eyes,\Nbut having friends and family...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:14.14,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,...may bring one happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.85,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,For us humans, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.67,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:20.20,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you consider happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.15,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:28.93,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be too greedy, but I guess being able to leave this flask would make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.80,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Immortality...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:45.49,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why fools who gained ultimate authority and prosperity begin to wish for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking to the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to be disrespectful, I'll break the flask!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:56.40,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to destroy the source of the knowledge you don't know about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.40,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,Cease your prattling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:03.41,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make me immortal or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.78,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Growing impatient as you age, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.94,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,How sad, King of Xerxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:15.84,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll tell you how to achieve immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.74,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're making a waterway for irrigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:27.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The King ordered a waterway to extend around the entire country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.85,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less to be expected from the King of Xerxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:33.44,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,He even thinks about commoners like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:43.54,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them all. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.45,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.42,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Waste no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:03.13,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and carve a bloody crest into the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The village to the north was raided?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:12.47,Default,Women,0000,0000,0000,,I heard everyone there was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And the same thing happened in the village to the west last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.75,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who's behind it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.85,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.77,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, how awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:44.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, the transmutation circle is finally complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:50.03,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, it has been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.57,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,This is all we need to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:57.64,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you'll be able to become immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.66,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.67,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,The King is going to become immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.90,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's what they call the turning point of the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.97,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,So this is immortality...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.52,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:59.82,Default,King,0000,0000,0000,,You said that since we're in the center of it, we wouldn't be harmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:06.42,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.62,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.43,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Homunculus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:17.24,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,The true center of the transmutation circle is where you're standing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.06,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:23.35,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I opened the gate using your blood inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:27.11,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,You're a relative that shares my blood, Hohenheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:31.79,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you and I are at the center of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:44.99,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.70,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.92,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.95,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.96,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Willard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:11.90,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Mechthild!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.74,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Linemile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:15.30,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Tony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.12,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Meiyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:31.81,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Someone, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:36.43,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. Everyone has had their souls taken from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:39.87,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:42.84,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You were all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:43.83,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:49.79,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,...How do you like your new body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.25,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It's... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:57.14,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I created a body for myself using\Nthe information stored in your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:03.04,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I can walk with my own two feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:08.06,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Homunculus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.69,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:15.69,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,In return for you giving me blood, I gave you a name and shared my knowledge with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.95,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,I also gave you an eternal body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.62,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:26.04,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Try focusing all of your consciousness into yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.61,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hear the voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:39.43,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,The voices of all the people, who lived in this country, sacrificed for your immortal body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:43.67,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, half of them went to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.70,Default,Homun,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help, Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:01.78,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hohenheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.57,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It really {\i1}is{\i0\fscx30} {\r} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:14.78,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I didn't know you were Ed and Al's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:17.96,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to be the master of my sons, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.26,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you did a lot for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:23.35,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:25.22,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.39,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Izumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.83,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get your medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:31.20,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take a look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:34.53,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I know a thing or two about medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:43.39,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, this isn't anything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.76,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,This is certainly something to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.74,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sig, please get a cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:50.53,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:52.25,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.77,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Izumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:02.11,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You saw the truth, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.86,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What did you sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:08.47,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't try to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.73,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They took a few of my organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:19.18,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to revive my dead baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.74,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:27.25,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:30.70,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.93,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.20,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:55.14,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Dear. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.94,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,You were stabbed in the stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:21:00.26,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,But I can breathe more easily now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:01.94,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.99,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.55,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:14.88,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,The organs that were taken are the proof of your sins, so I can't bring them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:18.96,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But I rearranged your insides a bit to ease the flow of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:23.34,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Izumi, you can't die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:26.63,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hohenheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:30.11,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just... what exactly {\i1}are{\i0\fscx30} {\r} you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:37.77,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a human by the name of Van Hohenheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:40.84,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,A philosopher's stone in human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:16.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Philosopher's Stone,\Nthe Heavenly Stone, the Great Elixir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how the philosopher's stone has many names,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:21.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,its form isn't always that of a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:25.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The one Doctor Marcoh had was almost like a gel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:31.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee's looked like a crystal, and it was about this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:35.55,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Since it possesses so much energy, I pictured something far larger...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:39.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen one bigger than a pebble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.29,0:23:46.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If it's something even larger, that would mean an enormous number of humans was used to create it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:51.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:02.50,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If one wishes to gain something,\None must present something of equal value.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.41,0:24:06.44,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That is the principle behind alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.44,0:24:09.38,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It is also the principle behind everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.46,0:24:15.05,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:18.11,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 41, Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.37,0:24:24.73,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His softness seeks pain from the boy as an equal exchange.
